==English==
===Pronunciation===
*stŏp, /stɒp/, /stQp/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-ɒp|Rhymes: -ɒp]]

===Verb===
'''to stop''' ([[stops]], [[stopped]], [[stopping]])

====Inransitive====
# to [[cease]] moving
#: ''I '''stopped''' at the traffic lights.''
# to come to an end
#: ''The riots '''stopped''' when it began to rain.''

